description: The fund seeks investment results that closely correspond, before fees and expenses, to the performance of the underlying index, which tracks the performance of US dollar denominated sovereign debt publicly issued by the US government in its domestic market with interest and principal payments tied to inflation, with a remaining term to final maturity of less than or equal to five years. The fund will invest at least 80% of its assets in securities included in the underlying index.
name: J.P. Morgan Exchange-Traded Fun
